=\"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/RootSystem/Defs.html#RootPairing.root\">root</a></span></span></span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">}</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Interval/Set/Defs.html#Set.Icc\">Set.Icc</a> <span class=\"fn\">q</span> <span class=\"fn\">p</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Note that it is often more convenient to use `RootPairing.root_add_zsmul_mem_range_iff` than\nto invoke this lemma directly. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/RootSystem/Chain.html#RootPairing.setOf_root_add_zsmul_eq_Icc_of_linearIndependent","kind":"theorem","line":44,"name":"RootPairing.setOf_root_add_zsmul_eq_Icc_of_linearIndependent","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/RootSystem/Chain.lean#L44-L98"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.RootSystem.Finite.Lemmas","Mathlib.Order.Interval.Set.OrdConnectedLinear"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.RootSystem.Chain"}